The getSummary method provides data about link profile of a website: a number of external links, referring IP addresses and subnets, a number of referring domains and subdomains, domain authority indicator and types of referring links.

The getRefDomains method provides a list of referring domains of a website you analyze. You will get this data: number of referring domains/subdomains/links, number of nofollow/dofollow links, domain rank, etc.
